      "content": "Hey, i'm working on a color palette for a new banking app. we want the vibe to be really calm and professional. the main brand color is a deep navy blue (hex #000080). can you suggest some complementary or analogous colors that would work well for a high-end corporate look? maybe some hex codes too? thanks.",
